miro
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Podocarpus ferrugineus</i> black pine (Otago) and its wood; a tall native forest tree with hard timber, aromatic foliage and red fruit. [Maori]
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: <i>Prumnopitys ferruginea</i>, previously <i>Podocarpus ferrugineus</i> aka bastard black pine
